column2: SELECT LTRIM (STR (mjd_r, #, #) ) AS MJD, dbo.fSDSS (p.objId) AS ID, modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g, modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r, modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i, p.ra, p.dec INTO #list FROM detectionindex d JOIN PhotoObjAll p ON d.objid = p.objid JOIN Field f ON p.fieldid = f.fieldid WHERE p.objid = # ORDER BY # -- -- Now find objects near each of the detections -- SELECT a.*, b.* FROM #list a CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (a.ra, a.dec, #) b
